## ğŸ“Š Monitoring (Bonus Implementation)

### Tools

* Prometheus
* Grafana

### Installation

```bash
helm install kube-prometheus-stack prometheus-community/kube-prometheus-stack \
  --namespace monitoring --create-namespace
```

### Metrics Observed

* Node CPU & Memory
* Pod health & restarts
* Application availability

